{
  "stem": "9701.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know there was food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wasn't hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess it wasn't really that important to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The thing that really troubled me is, where is my father?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where is my uncle?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where are all the men and boys?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My whole life had changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Also another thing that happened was Jewish children were no longer able to attend either public or private schools.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, you know, I had all this time on my hands.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I guess I was-- the main thing that I can remember is being afraid, terribly afraid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, if my mother moved from one chair to the other, where is she going?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How did you spend your time all those days?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, that's a good question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I cannot answer it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just-- all I remember is fear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think I was probably paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, not physically, but emotionally paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I don't remember doing anything except fear, fear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where is my father?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is he still alive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is he going to come back?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where is my uncle?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened to my other uncles?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What happened to my grandfather?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was no information about these men and boys who had been arrested and taken away for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then within a matter of a day or two, preprinted postcards arrived from the concentration camp Dachau, D-A-C-H-A-U.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dachau, by the way, was the first concentration camp that the Nazis constructed in 1933.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By November 1938 there were many others.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Jews who lived in different sections of Germany were sent to some of the other concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the Jews from where I lived sent to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a-- half of a postcard was preprinted.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
